"""Must specify status quo to have relative outcome constraint."""
ax_client = AxClient()
with self.assertRaises(ValueError):
    ax_client.create_experiment(name='test_experiment', parameters=[{'name':
        'x', 'type': 'range', 'bounds': [-5.0, 10.0]}, {'name': 'y', 'type':
        'range', 'bounds': [0.0, 15.0]}], objective_name='test_objective',
        minimize=True, outcome_constraints=['some_metric <= 4.0%'])
